"值时，就会出现漏洞。例如："
msgstr ""
"According to RFC 7230, when a server receives a request containing two "
"``Content-Length`` headers with different values, it should return a 400 "
"error. Some servers do not strictly implement this rule. In that case, if "
"the frontend and backend each use a different ``Content-Length`` value, a "
"vulnerability appears. For example:"

