msgstr ""
"TE-CL means the frontend server processes the ``Transfer-Encoding`` request "
"header, while the backend server processes the ``Content-Length`` request "
"header. For example:"

#: ../../source/vuln/httpSmuggling.rst:91
msgid "TE-TE"
msgstr "TE-TE"

#: ../../source/vuln/httpSmuggling.rst:92
msgid ""
"TE-TE指前后端服务器都处理 ``Transfer-Encoding`` 请求头，但是在容错性上表现不同，例如有的服务器可能会处理 "
"``Transfer-encoding`` ，测试例如："
msgstr ""
"TE-TE means both frontend and backend servers process the ``Transfer-"
"Encoding`` request header, but they differ in tolerance. For example, some "
"servers may process ``Transfer-encoding``. A test case is:"

